    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The complexity of this stored procedure is low. It involves a straightforward selection of data based on a few conditions and does not include any complex logic, loops, or multiple joins. The procedure consists of a single variable declaration, a simple query to set the variable, and a conditional selection query."
        }
